title: Why Vikings should be NFC North favorites over Packers (Football 05/08)
description:
Anthony Broome of 247 Sports joins Will Brinson to break down the Minnesota Vikings offseason, their draft, what to expect out of Kirk Cousins and John DeFillipo this coming season, whether the Vikings should be the favorites in the NFC North over the Packers and much more.
